turn.0: Annual State of the Sub Post: 'This is not the best Q&A Subreddit'
turn.1: TL;DR Please read the sidebar and search before posting.
turn.2: I earnestly mean it when I say that it is almost unfair that we are the most popular question sub and *also* the hardest to use.  The solution is that we get the other questions subs to pass us up so people can know them better.
